title: Free-Climbers Reach Summit Of Yosemite's El Capitan
teaser: After 19 days of climbing up a 3,000-foot rock face, gripping at granite sometimes no thicker than a dime, Tommy Caldwell and Kevin Jorgeson reached the top of El Capitan in Yosemite National Park.
